        "text": "let her be shorn",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") As the hinder part of the head is by nature in the man and the woman respectively, so in general it is becoming the forehead to be in its mode of dressing: ",
        "children": []
      },
