        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Corinthians 11:14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The imperative here is that of permission, but a permission, which has in it mimesis, or a deduction to something unsuitable.[91] So shaving is unbecoming in nuns.—",
        "children": []
      },
